com.bergerkiller.bukkit.common.inventory

Class InventoryBase

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.bergerkiller.bukkit.common.inventory.InventoryBase
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Iterable<org.bukkit.inventory.ItemStack>, org.bukkit.inventory.Inventory
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    InventoryBaseImpl, MergedInventory

    public abstract class InventoryBase
extends java.lang.Object
implements org.bukkit.inventory.Inventory
    A basic implementation of Inventory that excludes the getting and setting of item content information. Uses a backing CraftInventory to perform all utility methods provided by Bukkit. This ensures that the functionality is up-to-date with the latest bugfixes and additions.
